query:
SELECT 
  s.id as session_id, 
  s.status, 
  DATE(s.scheduledAt) as session_date,
  s.studentId,
  wl.id as workout_log_id,
  wl.sessionId as log_session_id
FROM sessions s
LEFT JOIN workout_logs wl ON wl.sessionId = s.id
WHERE s.status = 'completed'
ORDER BY s.scheduledAt DESC
LIMIT 10;
